Overview
Decade-old secrets reach the surface in a shocking trilogy that will change the life of ANT forever! Will Hannah be able to deal with the alarming truths behind her betrayal? Why does her returning memory threaten to end her very life? At a time like this, there's nobody better to have at your side than the SAVAGE DRAGON!
